<article class="row hentry post-270260 to4_video_post type-to4_video_post status-publish has-post-thumbnail category-interview tag-coronavirus tag-covid-19 tag-health-care-workers tag-new-york-city section-environment-and-health primary_topic-health" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ReportageNewsArticle">
<div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
<a class="archive-image" href="https://truthout.org/articles/health-care-workers-on-front-lines-of-covid-19-outbreak-lack-key-protections/" title="Health Care Workers on Front Lines of COVID-19 Outbreak Lack Key Protections">
<img width="400" height="300" src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1206647190-400x300.jpg" class="attachment-sd_medium size-sd_medium" alt="Nurses protest the Center for Disease Control&#039;s (CDC) weak response to the COVID-19 pandemic on March 11, 2020, outside the UCLA Medical Center in Los Angeles, California." loading="lazy" srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1206647190-400x300.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1206647190-200x150.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1206647190-800x600.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1206647190-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1206647190-2400x1800.jpg 2400w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" />
</a>
</div>
<div class="small-12 medium-8 columns archive-text">
<div class="before-headline">
<div class='categories'>
<a href='https://truthout.org/category/news/' rel='category' class='news'>News</a>
</div>
<div class='sections'>
<a href='https://truthout.org/section/economy-and-labor/' rel='section' class='economy-and-labor' style='color: #2c5b53;'>Economy &amp; Labor</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/health-care-workers-on-front-lines-of-covid-19-outbreak-lack-key-protections/">Health Care Workers on Front Lines of COVID-19 Outbreak Lack Key Protections</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">The lack of protections could create shortages of caregivers and undermine efforts to control the coronavirus.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/mike-ludwig/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Mike Ludwig</a></span>, </dd>
