<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/37000-more-americans-may-die-because-trump-did-not-take-covid-19-seriously/">37,000 More Americans May Die Because Trump Did Not Take COVID-19 Seriously</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">Trump&#8217;s inaction in early March may have cost the lives of tens of thousands of Americans, say epidemiologists.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/chris-walker/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Chris Walker</a></span>, </dd>
<dd class="source org" itemprop="sourceOrganization" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization"><span itemprop="name"><a href='https://truthout.org' itemprop='url'>Truthout</a></span></dd>
</dl>
